Applies to: monailabel==0.8.5, Python 3.10
File: E:\monailabel-env-310\lib\site-packages\monailabel\datastore\local.py

Problem 1: 3D Slicer sends image IDs like "1: 3D CBCT Image Set" which contain
colons — illegal characters in Windows filenames. This caused FileNotFoundError
on add_image and wrong path resolution in get_image_uri.

Problem 2: After server restart, datastore re-derives keys from sanitized
filenames, creating a mismatch with the original image IDs sent by Slicer.

Problem 3: CBCT DICOM studies in the studies folder were not found because
the local datastore only scans for NIfTI/NRRD extensions, not .dcm files.
